        title: "Local Business Directories.",
        descriptions: [
          "Local business directories like Yelp, Yellow Pages, Foursquare, Manta, and Chamber of Commerce listings are essential for local SEO. These platforms help your flight school appear in 'near me' searches and local map results.",
